Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.37,0:11:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(649.333,82.333)\c&H00181818\bord0}臨海露營場
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.69,0:11:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,然後是臨海露營場
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.37,0:11:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\p1\c&H00F8F8F8\bord3\3c&H00222320\\pos(646.933,89.533)}m 0 0 m 0 0 l 350 0 l 350 60 l 0 60
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.37,0:11:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(649.333,82.333)\c&H00181818\bord0}草地露營場
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.59,0:11:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,接著是草地露營場
